name: SQCDP - Safety, Quality, Cost, Delivery, People

rows.field_54307: Monitoring workplace safety and accident prevention.
Tracking financial efficiency and cost reduction.
Measuring on-time deliveries and production schedules.

fields.name: Last 30 avg
fields.formula: avg(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Value'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')))

fields.name: Last 30 count
fields.formula: count(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Value'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')))

fields.name: Last 30 sum
fields.formula: sum(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Value'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')))

fields.name: Last 30 min
fields.formula: min(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Value'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')))

fields.name: Last 30 max
fields.formula: max(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Value'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')))

fields.name: Last 30 symbols
fields.formula: join(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Judgement symbol'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('30 days')),' - ')

fields.name: Last 10 symbols
fields.formula: join(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Judgement symbol'),lookup('Daily updates','Date') >= today() - date_interval('10 days')),' - ')

rows.field_54320: The number of workplace accidents reported during a specific period.
Incidents that could have led to accidents but did not result in harm.
The total number of complaints received from customers regarding products or services.
The percentage of defective products identified in relation to the total produced.
The count of products or processes that fail quality inspections.
The total cost incurred in producing goods or services, including materials, labor, and overhead.
The total financial savings achieved through efficiency improvements or cost-cutting measures.
The percentage of deliveries made within the promised time frame.
The degree to which production or project timelines are followed as planned.
The average number of training hours completed per employee over a specific period.
The percentage of employees who leave the organization within a specific period.
The average score of employee or customer satisfaction surveys conducted over a period.

fields.name: Count occurences
fields.formula: count(filter(lookup('Daily updates','Judgement'),lookup('Daily updates','Judgement value') = field('Label value')))

fields.name: Label symbol
fields.formula: if(field('Label value') = 'Excellent','🟢',if(field('Label value') = 'Good','🟢',if(field('Label value') = 'Needs Improvement','🟡',if(field('Label value') = 'Unacceptable','🔴',''))))

fields.name: Judgement symbol
fields.formula: min(filter(lookup('Tresholds','Label symbol'),and(field('Value') >= lookup('Tresholds','Lower limit'),field('Value') <= lookup('Tresholds','Upper limit'))))
